Method: it is block/identifier, has number of instructions/statements which can perform a 
        specific task/activity.
        
Syntax of the method:
====================

for example, i am taking main() method. 

public static void main(String[] args) 
{
	System.out.println("Example1 class main() method");
} 

access modifier non access modifier return-type method-name(parameters)//method head/signature
{

	//method body/implementation

}


public: access modifier, other access modifiers are default(no keyword), private and protected.

static: non access modifier, other non access modifiers are final, abstract, synchronized..etc.


